title: Boys soccer: Zephyrs lose to Two Rivers | Local | presspubs.com
text:
The Mahtomedi boys lost to Two Rivers 4-2 on Wednesday. Abel Alumu led the victors with two goals and an assist. Mahtomedi is 4-5-1 overall and 2-2-1 in the Metro East. Two Rivers is 4-5-2 and 3-0-2.
